## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all possible income streams for independent filmmakers. The dynamic nature of the film industry means that new opportunities and challenges can arise, potentially affecting the relevance of the information over time. Additionally, the financial success of these alternative income streams can vary significantly based on individual skills, market demand, and geographic location.